[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0868","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0868.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1017","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9121,\"outputTokens\":18,\"totalTokens\":10803}}","description":"Seattle Labs Emurl 2.0 及早期版本将邮件附件存储在启用脚本执行权限的特定目录中，攻击者可发送包含恶意 ASP 脚本的邮件附件，诱导收件人打开邮件查看附件时触发服务器端 ASP 代码执行，导致远程代码执行。该漏洞影响 Seattle Labs Emurl 2.0 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 7.5（高危），攻击者需诱导用户打开恶意邮件附件即可触发远程代码执行，攻击门槛较低，危害严重。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1017"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-07-28T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:31.843","remediation":"升级 Seattle Labs Emurl 至已修复该问题的后续版本（2.0 以上官方补丁版），并修改邮件附件存储目录的 Web 服务器配置，禁用该目录的脚本执行权限（关闭 ASP 执行映射），同时配置邮件网关在投递前剥离或重命名可疑脚本类附件（如 .asp），作为无法立即升级时的临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93316253431588&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/544","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2126251525a2d370ea93bd7affc3a9b71b419b4c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1017.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1017","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1017.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d281505551869bb381f43b6d1c6cb3abf45ad885/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1017.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5d945305f2cad48b7bb06af582393a58c31555d3/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-h7mf-q457-42rj/GHSA-h7mf-q457-42rj.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/544/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1017.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/7fda9011502d7fc255ac49660ff374bd64965608/1999.tsv","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--ad9da5bf-aaaf-4798-bdc9-e24ced191d4e.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0868.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1684","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1684.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1018","title":"Linux 内核 IPChains IP 片段重叠绕过漏洞","description":"Linux 内核 2.2.10 及更早版本中的 IPChains 防火墙在重组 IP 分片前未对分片头部信息进行检查，导致远程攻击者可通过发送多个偏移量为 0 的恶意 IP 碎片绕过防火墙过滤规则。该漏洞影响使用上述内核版本并启用 IPChains 过滤机制的 Linux 系统，攻击者无需身份认证，只需向目标主机发送特制的重叠分片数据包即可规避访问控制策略，从而对受保护网络实施未授权访问或进一步攻击。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1018"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-07-27T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:31.960","remediation":"建议将 Linux 内核升级至 2.2.11 及以上版本（或 2.0.x 系列最新补丁版），该版本已修复 ipchains 未重组 IP 分片即检查头部导致的过滤绕过问题。如无法立即升级，可在防火墙规则中启用 IP 分片重组检查（如开启 net.ipv4.ipfrag_* 相关内核参数），并丢弃 offset 为 0 的异常重叠分片，临时缓解远程绕过过滤规则的攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93312523904591&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/543","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19301","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2126251525a2d370ea93bd7affc3a9b71b419b4c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1018.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1018","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1018.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d281505551869bb381f43b6d1c6cb3abf45ad885/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1018.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5d945305f2cad48b7bb06af582393a58c31555d3/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3xc5-vgfg-rqw3/GHSA-3xc5-vgfg-rqw3.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/543/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1018.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict","https://github.com/shamedgh/confine/blob/a75dad3ad336e6258a42cd1ce4af061eea68ed76/cve.files/cveToFile.json.type.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1684.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0406","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0406.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0710","title":"Squid cachemgr.cgi 未授权代理连接漏洞","description":"Squid 代理服务器在 Red Hat Linux 5.2/6.0 及其他发行版中默认将 cachemgr.cgi 脚本安装在公开可访问的 Web 目录下，导致未经身份认证的远程攻击者可利用该脚本作为跳板连接到内部或其他系统，造成信息泄露或进一步攻击。该漏洞影响 Squid 2.2 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。厂商已发布安全更新修复此问题。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0710"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-07-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:53.680","remediation":"升级 Squid 至 2.3 及以上版本，或删除或限制 cachemgr.cgi 文件的 Web 访问权限，仅允许受信任 IP 访问该脚本。在 Apache/Nginx 中配置访问控制，添加 `allow from 127.0.0.1` 和 `deny from all` 规则。如不使用缓存管理功能，直接移除 cachemgr.cgi 文件。同时启用 Squid 的缓存管理器认证功能，设置 `acl manager proto cache_object` 和 `http_access deny manager` 规则。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://fedoranews.org/updates/FEDORA--.shtml","http://www.debian.org/security/2004/dsa-576","http://www.redhat.com/archives/fedora-announce-list/2005-May/msg00025.html","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/RHSA-1999-025.html","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/RHSA-2005-489.html","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/archives/rh52-errata-general.html#squid","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/2059","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2385","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20465","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/cf29b986be3ae7c9144123b101d864868676099e/1999/CVE-1999-0710.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0612695ef658bcfcb0304f7ee1180b94e9117a85/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0710.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0710","https://github.com/microsoft/azurelinux/blob/5b41bff6ebaf7e8fc78637b564efee23b66e7d67/specs/s/squid/squid.spec","https://github.com/squid-cache/squid/blob/6f4c814b8181c38c56be817f2d339936b63b408f/ChangeLog","https://github.com/grafeas/grafeas/blob/448cd756a92f62111ecf96509c66267421396826/go/v1beta1/storage/testobjects.go","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/406e8eff8de253c79b1ce6440b2cb83ff8ecafd4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0710.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0710.md","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/fedora_2005-373.nasl","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1dbd44058e428445290bfb1f6fc6ecc0addbfd35/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qhrx-x4p7-jr4j/GHSA-qhrx-x4p7-jr4j.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0406.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0406.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0406.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0014","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0014.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0224","title":"Microsoft Windows NT Messenger Service 长用户名拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 Messenger 服务在解析超长用户名时存在边界处理缺陷，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可向目标系统发送特制的超长用户名数据包，触发服务崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞利用方式简单，攻击者无需复杂工具即可通过标准网络协议发包实施攻击，影响 Windows NT 4.0 全版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0224"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-07-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:56.923","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 针对 Windows NT 4.0 的 Service Pack 5 (SP5) 或更高版本，该补丁修复了 Messenger Service 对畸形用户名处理不当的问题。对于已停止支持的旧系统，建议升级至 Windows Server 2003 或更高版本；若无法升级，可在服务管理器中禁用 \"Messenger\" 服务以消除攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0224","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/329","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-0224.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0224.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0224","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0224.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0224.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0224.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0014.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0994","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0994.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1165","title":"GNU fingerd 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"GNU fingerd 1.37 存在权限管理缺陷，程序在访问用户信息前未正确放弃特权。本地攻击者可利用该漏洞通过两种方式实施攻击：一是在 .fingerrc 文件中放置恶意程序以获取 root 权限；二是利用 .plan、.forward 或 .project 文件中的符号链接读取系统任意文件。该漏洞影响运行 GNU fingerd 1.37 的系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。建议升级至最新版本或禁用 finger 服务。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1165"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-07-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:51.533","remediation":"建议立即禁用或卸载 finger 服务（如 `systemctl disable fingerd` 或 `apt remove fingerd`），该服务已过时且存在权限提升风险。如业务必须使用，应升级至修复了提权问题的版本，并确保 .fingerrc/.plan/.forward/.project 文件仅属主可写，同时以非 root 用户运行 fingerd 进程。作为临时缓解，可通过 `chmod 0 /usr/sbin/fingerd` 移除执行权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93268249021561&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/2478","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/535","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1d6385d398a2a41185d3cc14943c25f73c724ba3/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1165.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1165","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1165.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/baa4573f2fa6813cfbc3f5cda2f1796a92d64bdf/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1165.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/95e6ff620d5494b93ba2234edfcf6a45187dc0a8/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mgmg-j29c-p5ff/GHSA-mgmg-j29c-p5ff.json","https://github.com/illuusio/freebsd-osv/blob/3234f9e67d0170ff9c6cada9a1f48f061b109728/md/2007/FreeBSD-2007-0146.md","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/535/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1165.json","https://github.com/freebsd/freebsd-ports-gnome/blob/404a8a3dcfe44008a77681798d15e6d43285f73a/security/vuxml/vuln-2007.xml","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0994.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0808","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0808.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0810","title":"Samba 2.0.5 nmbd NETBIOS名称服务守护进程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Samba 2.0.5 版本的 NETBIOS 名称服务守护进程（nmbd）存在拒绝服务漏洞。该漏洞源于 nmbd 在处理特制的 NETBIOS 名称服务请求报文时，未能对输入进行充分校验，导致进程崩溃或进入异常状态。攻击者可向运行 nmbd 的服务器发送精心构造的恶意 UDP 数据包（目标端口通常为 137），远程触发服务不可用。影响范围涵盖使用 Samba 2.0.5 并启用 nmbd 进行 NetBIOS 名称解析与浏览服务的主机，攻击无需身份认证，属于远程可触发的拒绝服务。利用方式即向目标 nmbd 端口发送畸形名称服务请求，使其资源耗尽或崩溃，从而导致局域网内名称解析与浏览服务中断。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0810"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-07-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:06.230","remediation":"升级到 Samba 2.0.5a 或更高版本（推荐 2.0.7）。如无法立即升级，请在防火墙中限制 UDP 137/138 端口仅对可信内网开放，并移除 smb.conf 中所有 message command 配置行，然后重启 nmbd 服务使修复生效。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0810","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/73dad9db65989a09e468a4f3a98f0eea36f0346c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0810.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0810","https://github.com/fankh/vulnerability-poc/blob/8854c056beab250ba690e2bcc8887feb4c1f8139/1999/CVE-1999-0810/README.md","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0810.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/57cb981038a97031bd95a35a9b10bbed18ca4725/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0810.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vfc2-4x6j-g8gr/GHSA-vfc2-4x6j-g8gr.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0810.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--1c9eefb7-c050-43f6-af93-f95b6108af67.json","https://github.com/debiancn/debian.org/blob/6abc98daa6356b20e410013a6920b3764af682d4/english/security/1999/19990804.data"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0808.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0575","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0575.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0811","title":"Samba smbd 畸形消息命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Samba 是一款在 Linux/Unix 系统上实现 SMB/CIFS 协议的开源文件与打印共享服务软件。其核心守护进程 smbd 在处理客户端发送的畸形消息命令（message command）时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可构造超长或格式异常的消息命令数据包发送至开放 139/445 端口的 smbd 服务，触发栈缓冲区溢出，从而导致服务崩溃拒绝服务，在特定条件下甚至可执行任意代码并获得系统权限。该漏洞无需认证即可利用，威胁范围覆盖 2.0.5 之前的多个 Samba 版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0811"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-07-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:06.360","remediation":"建议立即升级 Samba 到 2.0.5 或更高版本，该版本已修复 smbd 程序处理畸形消息命令时的缓冲区溢出问题。如无法立即升级，应通过防火墙限制对 139/445 端口的访问，仅允许可信主机连接 SMB 服务，并在 smb.conf 中配置 hosts allow 白名单以减小攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/536","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19428","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/73dad9db65989a09e468a4f3a98f0eea36f0346c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0811.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0811","https://github.com/entrysky/mageni/blob/c58dcc9bc43b7fb267bb10a8083ada356fbc81d1/plugins/2020/samba/gb_samba_CVE-1999-0811.nasl","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0811.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/5297adfba5e91ee22e711c26c523b292d427c0d0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0811.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-c55w-jx2c-3c8x/GHSA-c55w-jx2c-3c8x.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/exploit.rules","https://github.com/jbeasl7/openvas-feed-sync-local/blob/fb27339bf790f38603dcf52a87a4652cadb30c7e/openvas-feeds/nvt-feed/2020/samba/gb_samba_CVE-1999-0811.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0811.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0575.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-01338","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-01338.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1338","title":"DeleGate 代理服务器 DGROOT 目录权限许可漏洞","description":"DeleGate 代理 5.9.3 及更早版本在 DGROOT 目录中创建的文件和目录具有全局可写权限，导致本地用户可修改或删除敏感文件","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1338"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-21","updated":"2024-06-16","remediation":"升级到 Delegate proxy 5.9.4 或更高版本，或手动修复 DGROOT 目录权限","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93259112204664&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-01338.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1183","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1183.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1560","title":"Texas A&M University Tiger 代码执行漏洞","description":"Texas A&M University (TAMU) Tiger 安全审计工具中的脚本存在代码执行漏洞，本地攻击者可利用脚本处理逻辑缺陷，以 Tiger 进程权限（通常为 root 权限）执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Tiger 早期版本，攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限，通过构造恶意输入触发脚本执行任意代码，导致权限提升至 root 权限，CVSS 评分 7.2，属高危本地提权漏洞。TAMU 已在后续版本中修复该脚本逻辑缺陷。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1560"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-20T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:43.110","remediation":"立即从 ftp://net.tamu.edu/pub/security/TAMU/ 下载并安装 Tiger 安全补丁，或升级到包含该补丁的最新版本。如无法升级，应限制不可信用户对系统的本地访问权限，并审查 Tiger 脚本中对用户输入的校验逻辑，确保所有外部参数经过正确过滤后再执行命令。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93252050203589&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2369","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/abfccbe3a11aa2b9dde2cfba5a12ba6256820a51/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1560.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1560","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-1560.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e1298ff7aafe81b936ca67ecef34c3124d6c72f0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1560.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/780ea229276a503f17a45c7ccc9fc5e26e6b2447/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-f2hg-7qhr-2xhq/GHSA-f2hg-7qhr-2xhq.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87935/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1560.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000702.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1183.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0408","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0408.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0721","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0/2000 Local Security Authority Subsystem 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 及 Windows 2000 系统的本地安全机构子系统（LSA）存在输入验证不当漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 LSA 请求报文，触发服务组件中的拒绝服务条件，导致 LSASS 进程崩溃、系统强制重启或域认证服务中断。该漏洞无需身份认证即可远程触发，影响 Windows NT 4.0 和 Windows 2000 全版本，CVSS 评分 7.8，危害等级高。Microsoft 已发布安全更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0721"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-07-20T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:55.073","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 于 1999 年发布的安全更新 KB242607（Windows NT 4.0）或升级至 Windows 2000 Service Pack 1 及以上版本。由于 Windows NT 4.0 和 Windows 2000 已停止支持，建议升级至受支持的 Windows Server 版本（如 Windows Server 2019/2022）。临时缓解措施可在防火墙层面限制对 LSA 端口的未授权访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ231457","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-049.shtml","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-020","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/64d76d92cfbd9c4de4a352a59a2e52cadebc3afd/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0721.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0721","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0721.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d2eb55660fa7a900eec90103b031be5d6f98d9ec/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0721.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1dbd44058e428445290bfb1f6fc6ecc0addbfd35/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hr94-mwmh-6848/GHSA-hr94-mwmh-6848.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0721.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0408.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1986","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1986.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1535","title":"Persits Software AspUpload 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Persits Software 公司开发的 AspUpload 组件中的 AspUpload.dll 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，影响 1.4.0.2 之前的所有版本。该组件通常用于 ASP 应用程序中处理浏览器文件上传功能，部署在 Windows NT 4.0 Server + IIS 3.0/4.0 等环境中。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向使用 AspUpload 的上传页面提交特制 HTTP 请求，在表单的文件名字段中输入 3800 个或更多字符的超长参数来触发缓冲区溢出，导致 IIS 的 inetinfo 进程崩溃终止，进而造成 Web 服务拒绝服务。在某些条件下，该漏洞还可能被利用以执行任意命令。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1535"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-20","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 Persits Software AspUpload 组件至 1.4.0.2 或更高版本，该版本已修复文件名字段缓冲区溢出问题；如无法立即升级，应移除或禁用 AspUpload 组件，并在前端上传页面限制文件名长度不超过合理范围（如 255 字符）以减轻拒绝服务风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93256878011447&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93501427820328&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/592","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3291"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1986.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1986.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1683","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1683.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1011","title":"Microsoft IIS MDAC RDS DataFactory 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"该漏洞存在于微软数据访问组件（MDAC）2.1中的远程数据服务（RDS）DataFactory组件中，该组件在IIS 3.x和4.x版本中暴露了不安全的调用方法。通过向目标系统发送特定的RDS请求，攻击者可以绕过权限验证，直接利用这些不安全的方法来执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响包括Microsoft IIS 3.0/4.0、Microsoft Index Server 2.0和Microsoft Site Server Commerce Edition 3.0等服务，能够在完全未授权的情况下实现远程代码执行。攻击者只需向目标服务器发送精心构造的RDS数据包，即可接管目标主机控制权，危害等级极高。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1011"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-07-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:31.110","remediation":"立即升级 MDAC 至 2.5 SP3 或更高版本（含 MDAC 2.6/2.7/2.8），或升级 IIS 至 5.0 及以上版本；若无法升级，请在 IIS 中禁用 RDS（删除 /msadc 虚拟目录、移除 msadcs.dll 注册表项、禁用 ADC/ADO/ADO MDAC 组件），并在防火墙层面封禁 TCP 80/443 端口对外暴露的 RDS 端点。立即应用微软安全公报 MS99-025 提供的补丁程序（MDAC 2.1 SP2 补丁 / IIS 4.0 补丁包）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-054.shtml","http://www.osvdb.org/272","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-004","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-025","https://www.securityfocus.com/bid/529","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19424","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/9a9b6476a3f4a52ffa21ec6ed80d737eb0fc242b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1011.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1011","https://github.com/fankh/vulnerability-poc/blob/8854c056beab250ba690e2bcc8887feb4c1f8139/1999/CVE-1999-1011/README.md","https://github.com/e-m-b-a/emba/blob/ffab8835dab57629dd708bbd389c0fd0b4f23ace/config/msf_cve-db.txt","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1011.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a6f1dc1488b4a75cccf07339e6a0f0ab45fc38ad/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1011.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/msadcs_dll.nasl","https://github.com/swimlane/soc-faker/blob/361c4ae88956878fbd8aaf5975044328556dfecd/socfaker/data/alert_names.txt","https://github.com/decal/werdlists/blob/81edb463f7f6311c85defefaf75ac9cd58e5cfb9/exploit-info/symantec-attack-signatures.txt","https://github.com/Chudry/Xerror/blob/07ec57cabcd27cdb47c89af452bdf4ed07207347/xerror/parsing/msf_module_result/msf_module_cve.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1683.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1683.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1683.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1092","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1092.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1378","title":"dbmlparser CGI 留言本程序任意文件读取漏洞","description":"dbmlparser.exe 是一款 CGI 留言簿程序，其 chroot 操作实现存在缺陷，导致 chroot 限制未能正确生效。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可利用路径遍历技术绕过目录隔离，读取服务器上的任意文件，包括配置文件、密码文件等敏感信息。该漏洞影响使用该 CGI 程序的 Web 服务器，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。由于该程序年代久远且已停止维护，建议迁移至其他受支持的留言簿解决方案。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1378"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:18.727","remediation":"立即停止使用 dbmlparser.exe 程序，该软件已停止维护且无安全更新。如必须运行，在 Web 服务器层面限制 CGI 脚本执行权限，仅允许访问特定数据目录；同时配置 Web 服务器（如 Apache 的 mod_rewrite 或 IIS 的 URL 重写）过滤 DBMLFILE 参数中的路径遍历字符（如 ../），并确保 CGI 进程以最低权限账户运行，限制其可读取的文件系统范围。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93250710625956&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1092.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0306","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0306.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0692","title":"Silicon Graphics IRIX Array Services daemon 认证绕过远程权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX（UNICOS）系统中 Array Services 守护进程（arrayd）的默认配置禁用了身份认证机制。未经身份验证的远程攻击者可以连接到目标系统的 arrayd 服务，利用该认证缺陷获取系统 root 权限，从而完全控制受影响的主机。该漏洞影响运行 Array Services 的 SGI IRIX/UNICOS 系统，攻击者无需任何凭据即可在远程执行特权操作，危害等级严重，CVSS 评分为 10.0。SGI 已在 1999 年 7 月的安全公告中发布修复补丁，建议管理员立即升级 arrayd 并启用身份认证配置。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0692"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-07-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:51.550","remediation":"建议将 Array Services daemon (arrayd) 的认证机制配置为 AUTHENTICATION NOREMOTE 或启用 PRIVATE_NETWORK 认证，编辑 /usr/lib/array/arrayd.auth 配置文件启用身份验证，禁止默认无认证配置。同时升级 SGI IRIX/UNICOS 至厂商提供的修复版本，并通过防火墙限制 arrayd 服务端口（默认 5434/tcp）仅对可信主机开放。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-052.shtml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e2e66cc19cc703324c2947fd6e7687a8b094f9fa/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0692.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0692","https://github.com/fankh/vulnerability-poc/blob/a15a199bf04146bf147bbda699ab0c4915229daf/1999/CVE-1999-0692/README.md","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0692.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/0f6f0e28732bc614273e91613aef04def1dce90b/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0692.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/c137f5e2e6bb5d0d49e919ecf3efde0b10d9a781/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-g2hc-xmvw-hhph/GHSA-g2hc-xmvw-hhph.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0692.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--9e4ef6a4-48d0-4517-8dd9-a548963a1dd4.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0306.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1700","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1700.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1086","title":"Novell NetWare IPX 数据包签名绕过权限提升漏洞","description":"Novell NetWare 5 及更早版本在 IPX 协议上运行时，若数据包签名级别低于 3，存在会话伪骗漏洞。远程攻击者可通过伪造 IPC 分片数据包中的 MAC 地址，冒充合法用户发送 NetWare 核心协议（NCP）调用，从而获取管理员权限。该漏洞无需身份认证，攻击者仅需处于同一 IPX 网络段即可实施攻击，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1086"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-07-15T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:41.520","remediation":"将 Novell NetWare 的数据包签名级别（Packet Signature Level）设置为 3 或更高，以强制 NCP 通信使用签名验证。升级到 Novell NetWare 6 及以上版本。在网络层面，对 IPX 协议的 IPC 分片数据包启用源地址验证，并限制可信 MAC 地址的 IPX 流量。如不再需要 IPX 协议，建议迁移至 TCP/IP 协议栈并禁用 IPX。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93214475111651&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/528"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1700.toml"}]